author: Discovery
description:
Last season, the moonshiners faced their toughest challenges yet, dodging law enforcement and rival crews while keeping their operations running. From Mark and Digger evading code enforcers to Mark and Huck seeking redemption, and Digger and Beaz risking it all on an elderberry mash, the stakes have never been higher!

About Moonshiners:
Every spring, a fearless group of men and women venture deep into the woods of Appalachia, defying the law, rivals and nature itself to keep the centuries-old tradition of craft whiskey alive.

description:
The crews head back under the ice, chasing gold in brutally cold water. Every dive means fighting breakdowns, bad weather, and the clock as they punch through shifting ice for one more shot at a real payday.
Don't miss #BeringSeaGold Fridays at 9P on Discovery!

#Discovery

About Bering Sea Gold:
In Nome, Alaska, the gold rush is on. Driven by gold fever and sometimes desperate need, miners pilot their ragtag dredges and dive with hoses to suck up gold from the bottom of the frigid, unpredictable Bering Sea.
